short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View and navigate all open tabs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This minimalist tab manager doesn't do a thousand things. It does one thing. Like a boss.
TabNabit shows you all your open tabs in a sorted table so you can quickly navigate to the one you want.
